      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个成绩同步流程的时序图。场景是Education_GradeSync核心模块处理同步任务，涉及UnitOfWork、Repository和MongoDB这几个关键组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
