    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下参与者：kikwi-core是主流程，UnitOfWork对应Education_ClassroomService，Repository是ProcessExecutionRepository，MongoDB是持久层，还有一个EventPublisher对应Education_LMS_Portal对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UoW",
