      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。流程开始是Core自己执行一些同步任务，然后创建UnitOfWork，传入Education_StudentDB上下文。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UoW",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出自循环的同步任务，然后是Core到UoW的创建调用。这里UoW会累积Education_LMS_Portal相关的变更。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "UoW",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "同步块结束后有个关键点：Core调用Repository的commit方法，把Education_LMS_Portal的数据提交。这里需要启动MongoDB事务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Repository",
        "MongoDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
